if any thing uploade or changes made tn the github it automatically triger the jenkins job so we use webhooks

To create a webhooks?
go to the github
go to the repository setting 
go to webhook and press add webhook  
go to Payload url in this past the jenkins url(ex:  http://3.568.658.658:8080/github-webhook)
go to Contant type in this seect application/x-www-form-urlencoded
go to the SSL verification in this select disableselect 
select active press create webhook

